                    <span class="bg-violet-400 text-xs text-white uppercase px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Design</span>
                    <h2 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-bold">10 Rules of Dashboard Design</h2>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Dashboard Design Guidelines.<h3>
